has attached great importance to it,

24
00:00:58,620 --> 00:01:00,220
often visiting the Archive
of the Three Judicial Departments

25
00:01:00,220 --> 00:01:01,660
to check on the progress
of the investigation.

26
00:01:02,100 --> 00:01:02,840
Wasn't the mastermind

27
00:01:02,840 --> 00:01:04,620
the Left Vice Minister
of the Ministry of Revenue?

28
00:01:04,620 --> 00:01:05,540
