34
00:01:16,620 --> 00:01:17,420
Suying.

35
00:01:20,740 --> 00:01:21,540
Furong.

36
00:01:23,220 --> 00:01:24,380
Why are you here?

37
00:01:28,620 --> 00:01:29,460
This is for you.

38
00:01:29,980 --> 00:01:31,740
