39
00:01:33,420 --> 00:01:35,020
Thank you for saving me yesterday.

40
00:01:36,940 --> 00:01:39,100
No worries. Thank you for your flowers.

41
00:01:39,700 --> 00:01:41,900
Oh, I also made
some nourishing tea for you.

42
00:01:42,700 --> 00:01:43,500
Suying.

43
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:47,540
I've brought back some delicious food
from the palace for you.

44
00:01:47,540 --> 00:01:48,940
Father wanted to host
a birthday banquet for me,

45
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:49,900
but I declined.

46
00:01:49,900 --> 00:01:50,820
Birthday banquet?

47
00:01:51,340 --> 00:01:52,740
Is it your birthday soon?

48
00:01:52,740 --> 00:01:54,540
Yes. It's coming up in a few days.

49
00:01:55,500 --> 00:01:57,420
What gift are you going to give me?

50
00:01:57,420 --> 00:01:58,620
What do you like?

51
00:01:58,740 --> 00:02:00,380
I'll like whatever you give me.

52
00:02:01,140 --> 00:02:03,020
Suying, I also want a gift.

53
00:02:03,020 --> 00:02:03,940
You want one too?

54
00:02:04,620 --> 00:02:05,860
But it's not your birthday.

55
00:02:06,140 --> 00:02:07,620
Can't I celebrate it today?

56
00:02:08,380 --> 00:02:10,380
Sure, you can celebrate it
any day you want.

57
00:02:13,180 --> 00:02:14,940
Since the last failed arrest,

58
