60
00:02:18,540 --> 00:02:19,380
We can only take it by storm.

61
00:02:19,980 --> 00:02:21,660
Now is not the time to take it by storm.

62
00:02:22,420 --> 00:02:24,340
Today is the Seventh Prince's birthday,

63
00:02:24,780 --> 00:02:25,790
