64
00:02:25,790 --> 00:02:27,100
to investigate
the identity of that maid.

65
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:28,420
I'll dispatch someone right away...

66
00:02:28,420 --> 00:02:29,180
No need.

67
00:02:29,380 --> 00:02:30,700
It might alert them.

68
00:02:32,980 --> 00:02:35,220
Since the maid is in the mansion,

69
00:02:35,340 --> 00:02:37,420
I'll personally go
and meet her to find it out.

70
00:02:39,380 --> 00:02:40,740
You've solved the case

71
00:02:40,740 --> 00:02:41,900
and today's your birthday.

72
00:02:42,140 --> 00:02:43,500
It's truly two happy events
happening at the same time.

73
00:02:43,660 --> 00:02:46,180
But why don't you
host a banquet at home

74
00:02:46,180 --> 00:02:47,460
and invite guests over to celebrate?

75
00:02:47,460 --> 00:02:49,420
